Gtk2-Ex-TimeEntry version 0.04
==============================

An entry widget for inputting that time of the day.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Gtk2

